l (6m3 early) Pressure up to 18mpa to set slips set 50KdaN compression on string to set slips. Bled off pressure. Set string in 10kdan compression turn string 5 turns to the right to Disengage setting tool. Rotate off liner hanger with 20 clockwise turns (3800ft/lbs torque) Pressure up liner to 2mpa, Picked up .5m to confirn we were off Liner hanger, come down and set string in 40 kdans compression. Pressured liner up to 30mpa to shear landing seat. Circulate at .5m3 until cementers are ready.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"08:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"09:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 1.0,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting with cementers\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"09:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"09:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Rig in cementers, pump 1m³ Opti, pressure test lines to 55mpa, Pump 9m³ Opti @ 1350kg/m3, Followed by 36.26m³ cement @ 1850kg/m³, flush surface lines.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"09:15\",\n      \"end_time\": \"12:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 3.0,\n      \"activity\": \"launch landing dart, pump 44.27m³ of inhibited water Bumped plug 5mpa over FCP., Hold for 5 min. bleed off check floats. (good) rig out cementers, Come off liner top packer, circulate out excess cement, displace annulas to inhib water\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"12:15\",\n      \"end_time\": \"14:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 2.5,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting prior to tripping out of hole\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"14:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"15:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Trip out of hole from 2994m to 0m\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\":