 pumps and hoses\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"05:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"05:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting with rig crew + Welders prior to welding bowls\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"05:15\",\n      \"end_time\": \"06:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 1.0,\n      \"activity\": \"Weld on casing bowl\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"06:15\",\n      \"end_time\": \"06:30\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting / Crew change - With Rig Manager and ARC Rep, LSR - Hot work\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"06:30\",\n      \"end_time\": \"07:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 1.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Weld on casing bowl\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"07:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"08:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting prior to Nippling up\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"08:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"16:30\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 8.5,\n      \"activity\": \"Nipple up BOPs, install bowl valves, install speed head, install kill valves, HCR valves, choke lines, Flare and degasser lines\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"16:30\",\n      \"end_time\": \"18:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 1.5,\n      \"activity\": \"Nipple up MPD\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"18:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"18:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Pressure Test BOP, Upper rams, lower rams, blind rams, All Inside and outside choke and kill v