kpa pressure bled to 2600kpa in 15min bump pressure back up to 3000kpa and held for 15 min.", "activity": "Squeeze Cement", "depth_md": 563.0, "end_time": "15:15", "start_time": "15:00", "page_number": 9, "duration_hours": 0.25}, {"comment": "Rig Service - functioon test upper and lower pipe rams closed 8 seconds each.", "activity": "Rig Service", "depth_md": 563.0, "end_time": "16:00", "start_time": "15:15", "page_number": 9, "duration_hours": 0.75}, {"comment": "Circulate above cement plug w/ rig pumps. 4m3 spacer and 0.5m3 cement returns to surface.", "activity": "Cond Mud & Circ", "depth_md": 563.0, "end_time": "17:45", "start_time": "16:00", "page_number": 9, "duration_hours": 1.75}, {"comment": "Drill loss circulation cement plug from 614m to 852m @ 1.5m3/min / 30rpm / 120m/hr controlled ROP (1-3kdan WOB seen at this speed)", "activity": "Drill Actual", "depth_md": 852.0, "end_time": "18:45", "start_time": "17:45", "page_number": 9, "duration_hours": 1.0}, {"comment": "Safety meeting - crew change handover", "activity": "Safety Meeting", "depth_md": 852.0, "end_time": "19:00", "start_time": "18:45", "page_number": 9, "duration_hours": 0.25}, {"comment": "Making connections from derrick", "activity": "Other", "depth_md": 852.0, "end_time": "21:45", "start_time": "19:00", "page_number": 9, "duration_hours": 2.75}, {"comment": "Rig Service change out grabber dies and functioned annular closed in 19 seconds.", "activity": "Rig Service", "depth_md": 852.0, "end_time": "10:30", "start_time": "10:15", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.25}, {"comment": "Run in hole open ended from surface to 850m (Plug depth.)", "activity": "Trips", "depth_md": 850.0, "end_time": "11:15", "start_time": "10:30", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.75}, {"comment": "Condition mud & circulate while rigging in Trican.", "activity": "Cond Mud & Circ", "depth_md": 850.0, "end_time": "11:30", "start_time": "11:15", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.25}, {"comment": "Safety meeting with Trican, DC crew and ARC OSS prior to pumping plug.", "activity": "Safety Meeting", "depth_md": 850.0, "end_time": "11:45", "start_time": "11:30", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.25}, {"comment": "Rig in Trican", "activity": "Other", "depth_md": 850.0, "end_time": "12:00", "start_time": "11:45", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.25}, {"comment": "Circulate the hole clean staging the pump up from 1.5m3/min to 2.15m3/m3 with no losses", "activity": "Cond Mud & Circ", "depth_md": 852.0, "end_time": "22:15", "start_time": "21:45", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.5}, {"comment": "Perform FIT. Stage the pump up to 1400kpa surface applied pressure to simulate 1280kg/m3 for 15min with 80kpa pressure loss. (good test) Bleed off pressure to drill ahead", "activity": "Test BOP", "depth_md": 852.0, "end_time": "22:45", "start_time": "22:15", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.5}, {"comment": "Drill 222mm intermediate hole from 852m to 939m", "activity": "Drill Actual", "depth_md": 939.0, "end_time": "23:45", "start_time": "22:45", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 1.0}, {"comment": "Accumulated off bottom time while drilling", "activity": "Other", "depth_md": 939.0, "end_time": "24:00", "start_time": "23:45", "page_number": 10, "duration_hours": 0.25}], "well_name": "7GEN HZ 102 KAKWA 16-33-62-4", "bit_records": [{"hours": null, "comment": "GTD65DK", "bit_size": 222.0, "depth_in": 0.0, "depth_out": 852.0, "bit_number": "1"}, {"hours": null, "comment": "GTD65DK", "bit_size": 222.0, "depth_in": 852.0, "depth_out": 939.0, "bit_number": "2"}], "mud_records": [{"ph": 7.5, "comment": "PREMIX TANK", "depth_md": 680.0, "viscosity": 29.0, "mud_weight": 1000.0}, {"ph": 7.5, "comment": "PREMIX TANK", "depth_md": 680.0, "viscosity": 29.0, "mud_weight": 1010.0}, {"ph": null, "comment": "PREMIX", "depth_md": 852.0, "viscosity": 30.0, "mud_weight": 1050.0}, {"ph": null, "comment": "Shakers", "depth_md": 745.0, "viscosity": 43.0, "mud_weight": 1050.0}], "surfac