 to surface, chained down casing and displace with 24.97m³ Fresh H20. Bump plug Feb 21, 2023 at 06:15hrs. Bleed back 100 L. Checked Floats - OK. 28m³ of good cement returns. 0 annulus Fall back.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"6:30\",\n      \"end_time\": \"6:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Rig out cement head & lines\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"6:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"7:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Crew change hand over meeting. Discussed ongoing tasks, hazard IDs and observations with crews, rig managers and ARC rep. Lifesaving rule-confined space\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"7:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"9:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 2.0,\n      \"activity\": \"Continue rig out to cement casing/ trash pumps prep cellar to cut casing\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"9:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"11:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 2.0,\n      \"activity\": \"CAT casing, weld on casing bowl\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"11:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"11:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting prior to nipple up BOP, review CTA 5-2.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"11:15\",\n      \"end_time\": \"15:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 4.5,\n      \"activity\": \"Nipple up BOP, install / secure stack on casing bowl, install flow line & choke lines to manifold, install beyond valves back onto top of stack, install hydraulic hoses and flow line. Fold down walkways and install grating after arriving mop bouts into position.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"15:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"16:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting prior to pressure testing BOP, review CTA 5-3.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"16:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"18:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 2.75,\n      \"activity\": \"Pressure test annular high 10500kpa. 1400 kpa low 10 min each, test upper & lower pipe rams, blind rams .2 working scoops, HCR valves x4, kill line valves x4, check valves x 2, kill line hoses x 2, bowl & valves x2, choke lines to manifold, manifold valves, stabbing valve inside. BOP & lower kelly valve @ 1400kpa low/ 34000kpa high 10min each. Remote choke x 2 7000k.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"18:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"19:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Crew change hand over meeting. Discussed ongoing tasks, hazard IDs and observations with crews, rig managers and ARC rep. Lifesaving rule-safe mechanical lifting\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"19:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"22:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 3.75,\n      \"activity\": \"Cont. pressure test BOP''s\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"22:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"23:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Function test accumulator, starting pressure 21000kpa, close annular 20secs, and close upper pipe rams 5secs, close lower pipe rams 5secs, open HCR 2secs. remaining pressure after 4 functions 10000kpa, recharge 2 min 37secs, precharge 7000kpa. n2 bottles - 6x2100psi.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"23:00\",\n      \"end_time\": \"23:15\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Install wear bushing\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"23:15\",\n      \"end_time\": \"23:30\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Rig service / service top drive\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"23:30\",\n      \"end_time\": \"23:45\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Pre-spud safety meeting, hazard hunts, drops inspection zones 1-4.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    },\n    {\n      \"start_time\": \"23:45\",\n      \"end_time\": \"24:00\",\n      \"duration_hours\": 0.25,\n      \"activity\": \"Safety meeting prior to making up BHA, review CTA 2-1.\",\n      \"depth_md\": null,\n      \"comment\": null,\n      \"page_number\": 1\n    }\n  ],\n  \"mud_records\": [\n    {\n      \"depth_md\": 633.0,\n      \"mud_weight\": 140.0\n    }\n  ],\n  \"deviation_surveys\": [],\n  \"bit_records\": [\n    {\n      \"bit_number\": \"2\",\n      \"bit_size\": 222.0,\n      \"depth_in\": 0.0,\n      \"depth_out\": 633.0,\n      \"hours\": 49.0\n    }\n  ]\n}"}','{"time_logs": [{"comment": null, "activity": "Run 49 Joints of 244mm, 53.57kg/m, J-55, LTC Casing with Weatherford Float equipment and 18 Bowspring Centralizers from surface to 633m", "depth_md": null, "end_time": "1:45", "start_time": "0:00", "page_number": 20, "duration_hours": 1.75}, {"comment": null, "activity": "Install circulating head - circulate casing", "depth_md": null, "end_time": "3:30", "start_time": "1:45", "page_number": 20, "duration_